  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A fast paced explosive experience!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This fast paced platformer without jumping (inspired by donkey kong's country barrel sections and downwell!) rewards quick thinking and good reflexes as you blast your way through rocks collecting <strong>precious gems</strong> to unlock the next <strong>sections</strong>, <strong>gamemodes</strong> and <strong>color Palettes</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/a5bfdc537b36cc6f6e0568eee8233020.poster.avif?t=1738326738\" width=506 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/a5bfdc537b36cc6f6e0568eee8233020.webm?t=1738326738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/a5bfdc537b36cc6f6e0568eee8233020.mp4?t=1738326738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>It's not rocket science... or is it?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blasting from barrel to barrel is fun and all, but ROCKETS are even better! Ride on top of precarious rocket barrels while skillfully dodging mineral worms, one eyed bats and pointy rocks in your way, but be careful because these flimsy rockets have a tendency to explode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/7c57928060e95c1dd5abb4bfde321ae2.poster.avif?t=1738326738\" width=506 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/7c57928060e95c1dd5abb4bfde321ae2.webm?t=1738326738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/7c57928060e95c1dd5abb4bfde321ae2.mp4?t=1738326738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pickaxes Are bouncy now?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As weird as it sounds, your pickaxe do be bouncing! When timed properly red slopes will redirect your momentum, just press the spacebar right before touching the slope. Sounds easy enough, but getting the timing right can be tough as nails in some sections!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/51089cc9bd36cdaf00d02de70405fe6e.poster.avif?t=1738326738\" width=506 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/51089cc9bd36cdaf00d02de70405fe6e.webm?t=1738326738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/51089cc9bd36cdaf00d02de70405fe6e.mp4?t=1738326738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A fast paced explosive experience!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This fast paced platformer without jumping (inspired by donkey kong's country barrel sections and downwell!) rewards quick thinking and good reflexes as you blast your way through rocks collecting <strong>precious gems</strong> to unlock the next <strong>sections</strong>, <strong>gamemodes</strong> and <strong>color Palettes</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/a5bfdc537b36cc6f6e0568eee8233020.poster.avif?t=1738326738\" width=506 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/a5bfdc537b36cc6f6e0568eee8233020.webm?t=1738326738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/a5bfdc537b36cc6f6e0568eee8233020.mp4?t=1738326738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>It's not rocket science... or is it?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blasting from barrel to barrel is fun and all, but ROCKETS are even better! Ride on top of precarious rocket barrels while skillfully dodging mineral worms, one eyed bats and pointy rocks in your way, but be careful because these flimsy rockets have a tendency to explode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/7c57928060e95c1dd5abb4bfde321ae2.poster.avif?t=1738326738\" width=506 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/7c57928060e95c1dd5abb4bfde321ae2.webm?t=1738326738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/7c57928060e95c1dd5abb4bfde321ae2.mp4?t=1738326738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pickaxes Are bouncy now?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As weird as it sounds, your pickaxe do be bouncing! When timed properly red slopes will redirect your momentum, just press the spacebar right before touching the slope. Sounds easy enough, but getting the timing right can be tough as nails in some sections!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/51089cc9bd36cdaf00d02de70405fe6e.poster.avif?t=1738326738\" width=506 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/51089cc9bd36cdaf00d02de70405fe6e.webm?t=1738326738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813560/extras/51089cc9bd36cdaf00d02de70405fe6e.mp4?t=1738326738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
